name: Crypto Relief Package Dao
description: Now gather a group of blockchain punks to speak for the world's poor children, to show love for poor children, and to give more children a fair opportunity. We create a blockchain project. Crypto Relief Package Dao is completely dominated by the world community and belongs to the community autonomous DAO model. Crypto Relief Package Dao will collect ETH through JuiceBox, and each participant will contribute ETH and get a corresponding share of governance tokens Contributed ETH distribution: 50% is donated to UNICEF, 30% is used for market value management and community rewards, 10% is listed on at least 3 centralized exchanges in the top 5, and 10% is marketing funds, we will never Give up, grow with all community members, grow with the children of the world
payDisclosure: Thank you for supporting UNICEF and the crypto world
